	<dl>
	<dt>There is no "None of the Above" box ...</dt>
	<dd><p>There is no "None of the Above" box on the voting slip. I would vote if a majority voted for "None of the Above" forced another election in that constituency with the existing candidates not allowed to stand.</p>
	<small>
	written 27th Apr 2005 <!--  | <a href="../email/1509">Email this
    to a friend</a> | <a
    href="/abuse/?postid=1509">abusive?</a> -->
	</small>
	</dd>
	</dl>

